  "_comment": "Controlled vocabulary for the genre-specification classifier. Edit freely: the Claude classifier is constrained to these values and must return genre='other' with a free-text suggested_label when nothing fits, rather than inventing a label. 'energy' and 'vibe' are flat enums; 'genres' maps each allowed genre to its allowed subgenres. Catalog spans American, European and Latin music — no region is dominant. After editing, re-run `python cli.py genre-classify --all --reclassify` to re-tag.",
